            <title>店猫 AirTag 都有人偷，旺角知名店猫遇贼、贼人行踪曝光</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/airtag-11/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=airtag-11</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/airtag-11/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 08:27:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AirTag]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305346</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在旺角一带广受欢迎的药房店猫「阻 B」，近日不幸成为小偷目标。牠身上专为防止走失或被拐走而配戴的 Apple AirTag 竟然遭人偷走，引发网民关注。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8184-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8184-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8184-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8184-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>「阻 B」一向习惯穿著一条轻便猫绳，绳带上设有一个小袋子，里面放置了 AirTag，以便主人可以随时掌握牠的动向。但近日有不法之徒竟趁隙将这个小袋子内的 AirTag 偷走，留下仍在街头巡游的「阻 B」，而定位器却已失去联系。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8186.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8186-694x512.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="512" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8186-694x512.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8186.jpg 1220w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲平时「阻 B」的猫带上都有小袋子装有 AirTag（图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1heor9g xkrqix3 x1sur9pj x1pd3egz" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/cat.cat.manager2/">香港猫店长关注组 2.0</a>）</p><p>今日「阻 B」的 Instagram 帐户上，主人上载了 AirTag 追踪画面，显示 AirTag 最后一次出现的位置是港岛西坚尼地城一带，但目前已无法连接，定位资讯也停止更新。主人在贴文中无奈写道：「AirTag 都好偷」，配上无奈表情符号，呼吁大家关注。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8183-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305350" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8183-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8183-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_8183-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>主人也分享了一张特制图片「阻 B」双手举著牌子，上面写著「边个偷咗我个 AirTag？」，表达对事件的不满与无奈。</p><p>这次事件引起不少爱猫人士热议，不少人担心即使为宠物配备防走失设备，也未必能完全防止意外，甚至引来有心人士趁机行窃。有人更批评偷窃者行为恶劣。</p><p>资料来源：Facebook</p><br /><b>
]]>
